To create a favicon for ToolDash:

1. Create a simple icon with the lightning bolt ⚡ symbol
2. Use a dark background with blue/cyan accent colors
3. Save as favicon.ico (16x16, 32x32, 48x48 sizes)
4. Place in the root directory

For now, browsers will use the default favicon behavior.
You can generate a favicon at: https://favicon.io/favicon-generator/